name: Mutable OBJKT 1
description:
This OBJKT is special. Each time you burn one, you add something to the canvas.

Before burning, adjust the last 4 digits of the baker fee. The baker fee you use will determine how you change the canvas.

The baker fee format for this OBJKT is as follows:

0.00xywh tezos

So, if you use a baker fee of 0.004355, you will draw a rectangle at coordinates x=4, y=3 with width=5 and height=5.

Zero width or height will draw a line. Zero width and zero height will draw a circle.

The color is unique to your wallet address.
